         <div type="translation">
            <p>
               <choice corresp="#a1">
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">... 2. || The king says: « ...</seg></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#a2">
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">Rejoiced he went into the divine world.</seg></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#a3">
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">... king (?). || There now out of faith ...</seg></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#a4">
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">... He now is Sun(darananda ?) ...</seg></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#a5">
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">... they fixed ... in the deeds.</seg></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#b1">
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">... king Subhāṣitagaveṣiṃ ...</seg></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#b2">
                  <seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>203</citedRange></bibl></seg>
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">... you have made me ... Through your hope now ...</seg></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#b3">
                  <seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1995"/><citedRange>53</citedRange></bibl></seg>
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">... the many terrible armies of the (passions). Your ...</seg></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#b4">
                  <seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:krause1952"/><citedRange>144</citedRange></bibl></seg>
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">... you will scatter without remnant; you will make their front yield.</seg></seg>
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">… you will scatter (their armies?) completely and make their front give way …  (cf 144)</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:peyrot2013b"/><citedRange>666</citedRange></bibl></seg>
               </choice>
               <choice corresp="#b5">
                  <seg><seg type="prim_transl">... out of ... I will point out to him; I will says this ...</seg></seg>
               </choice>
            </p>
         </div>
